{"tid":1059370,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"高圖爾斯父：兒子被傳媒欺凌","createTime":"2019-03-13T05:34:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-13T05:47:18.000Z","uid":153600,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"dbc17f17283d7f569c8833b52ba2cc9437130321","tid":1059370,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T05:34:51.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=WTugOjWmLb2R3dS25JBA%2BYPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=605cce1a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】皇家馬德里門將泰拔高圖爾斯的父親公開表示，兒子在西班牙受到欺凌。<br />\n<br />\n皇家馬德里今季演出失色，連帶新加盟的門將泰拔高圖爾斯（Thibaut Courtois）失球不少，早前更於歐聯16強次回合主場失掉4球予阿積士，包括被對方中場舒奧尼在窄位笠入罰球，表現備受批評。<br />\n<br />\n「我認為所有人都以泰拔為目標，包括西班牙傳媒。作為父親，我不能夠坐視不理。」迪亞利為兒子申冤。「門將永遠都是首個目標，這是工作的一部份，批評是對是錯，就讓大家去評論好了。」<br />\n<br />\n迪亞利指高圖爾斯對阿積士失了那記罰球，大家就忘記了他整場都踢得很好：「傳媒發放了很多關於泰拔私人事的新聞，我知道他們的用意。幸好，他並沒有受到影響。」高圖爾斯早前與模特兒一起用膳，被傳媒大做文章。"},{"pid":"787c71dfb195951c7d04dc6d0cbc41756e43e34b","tid":1059370,"uid":201731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T05:35:46.000Z","msg":"廢"},{"pid":"1e04d168a19961e23d8387ed0764990680f169a7","tid":1059370,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T05:37:10.000Z","msg":"25仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f416910dae0a96d6d77ed50f3586497050d2cc6","tid":1059370,"uid":35547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T05:37:30.000Z","msg":"你個仔話好想返黎馬德里住架wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"127adbdf3f8746d742197800e449d7b8ab76ce33","tid":1059370,"uid":170733,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T05:40:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tSxNgBr.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtSxNgBr.gif&h=f0bd35f7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"abeec7c9b34be61c09389c47a0afa2cb91f06f08","tid":1059370,"uid":166474,"like":1,"dislike